<paragraph blockId="11.[211,1172,1604,1699]" box="[211,331,1604,1628]" pageId="11" pageNumber="1267">
<heading box="[211,331,1604,1628]" fontSize="10" level="3" pageId="11" pageNumber="1267" reason="5">
<emphasis box="[211,331,1604,1628]" italics="true" pageId="11" pageNumber="1267">Etymology</emphasis>
</heading>
</paragraph>
<paragraph blockId="11.[211,1172,1604,1699]" pageId="11" pageNumber="1267">
The specific name “marina” is in honour of my mother Marina 
<collectingCountry box="[928,1001,1643,1667]" name="Indonesia" pageId="11" pageNumber="1267">Flores</collectingCountry>
. This is a noun in apposition, gender feminine.
</paragraph>
